				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't have this AA (yet), but if it's indeed a straight +3% chance per level I would say that levels 2 and 3 are really overpriced.
<br />

<br />
First 3% you get for 5AA (1.7AA/1%)
<br />
Next 3% you get for 10AA (3.3AA/1%)
<br />
and the last 3% you get for 15more AAs (5AA/1%)
<br />

<br />
So unless you really have no clue what to put your AAs into, it seems as if lvl2 and lvl3 of this ability really is extremly expensive compared to lvl1.
<br />
Now...the 3% of lvl1 hardly make a noticeable difference, ...but at least the return you get for it is somewhat cost-effective ;-)</span></td>
