				<td colspan="2"><span>I have 2 ranks in this and they were well worth it, for both Chant and up till the 13th, for AE kiting, yes this AA works on the PBAE dots as well.
<br />

<br />
Made for much, much faster AE kites with so many crits going off each tick, with a 20 mob kite it was unusual not to see 2 or 3 crits per tick with 3 dots running.
<br />

<br />
It's very nice in chant and swarm kiting as well, knocks mobs down noticably faster.  In straight chant kiting it nocks about 1 minute of a previously 6 minute kite, not much you might think but it does add up.  In an AE kite it knocked a good 3 minutes off the 19 minute kite time.. more time to give the fingers a break between pulls or gather more mobs for the next kite.  Level 3 seems bloated, saving the rest of my AA's for OoW.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
